window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The last thing I expected was to gain the spells of the woman in my bed.</b></p> <p>Hell, I didn't even know magic existed until I'd cast a spell that morning. Then a beautiful teacher from a magical academy told me I could become the universe's most powerful mage. To get there, I need to become stronger. I need to ace all my examinations. And, most of all, I need to master the most potent spells.</p> <p>But I have to start somewhere.</p> <p>This begins my first year at the Mazirian Academy.</p>"; 
